    "This approach aimed to facilitate the application of the findings to similar studies within the same context.",
    "To ensure confirmability, preliminary findings were shared with the participants, and verbatim quotations were incorporated to allow participants to confirm whether the presented information accurately reflected their views.",
    "As for dependability, the researcher sought assistance from a second researcher to analyse the data.",
    "After the data was independently analysed by both researchers, the findings of this study were compared for consistency and reliability.",
    "This study aimed to explore postgraduate students' perceptions of the benefits associated with the utilisation of artificial intelligence tools, with a specific focus on ChatGPT, for their academic success at historically disadvantaged universities in South Africa."
